{
  "stem": "3638.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So first it was they take care of the weapon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they take care of the food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they took care of the furs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then they took care of the jewelry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Systematically, they make the Jews poorer and poorer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when they make them poor, then they shift them from one place to another till they brought them to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they exterminate them from the ghetto to there-- it was a-- it was a organized, systematical-- systematic extermination, put it this way.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not if I know, but-- nobody had-- not-- not-- not what I know had anybody weapons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wouldn't jeopardize the family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but even before the Germans came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, nobody had a weapon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we left Krakow and we went to Velichka.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't go because we-- we went out on the [? cart, ?] because my-- my-- my father's brother, with the children, were living there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uncle, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, Jakob Armer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a younger brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had 11 children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we went there because this uncle had only one son.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the German came into Velichka, right from the beginning, the first few weeks, they rounded up 50 Jews.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And between the 50 Jews was my uncle and his older son.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took them outside Velichka and they shot them for no reason.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was just the auntie with the children left and a business to run.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my father, we went over there together, you know, to help them as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my younger brother, because my older brother was somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my sister, her husband, and a child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something like that.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
